  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The breakfast service runs from 7am until 11.30am and offers a rich and varied continental buffet with special hot options available such as sausages, bacon, pancakes and eggs. Dinner is served here for those of half board and is also a buffet service with plenty of choice and a heavy influence of traditional Sicilian cuisine using fresh and local ingredients wherever possible.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
