  <description><![CDATA[<p>You’ll find the modern Hotel Acacia Marina nestled in 20,000 square metres of tropical gardens on <a data-udi="umb://document/aafdbd88af954166b49b0bd7fa839f19" href="/{localLink:umb://document/aafdbd88af954166b49b0bd7fa839f19}" title="South East Sicily">Sicily</a>’s southern coast. With several small coastal towns within walking distance and the Mediterranean Sea just 100 yards away, this four star property offers ultimate comfort and relaxation. Each of the rooms are soundproofed and feature contemporary décor along with great amenities. There are two restaurants on site, one included within half board and the other providing a selection of a la carte dishes (payable locally). Surrounded by luscious and verdant gardens, the hotel pool spans an impressive 400 square metres and an outdoor hot tub can also be found close by providing the perfect spot to kick back and relax in the Sicilian sunshine. The hotel is also home to a private beach where golden sands slope gentle down to the crystalline waters and sun loungers (payable locally) are scattered throughout the looming palms. On the days when you need to get away from it all, take a trip to the hotel spa (payable locally) and immerse yourself in pure relaxation.</p>
<p>Car hire is recommended for this hotel. Hotel Acacia Marina is approx. 1 hour 40 mins from Catania Airport</p>]]></description>
