  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Rooms </strong>sleep up to four people and measure 23m². They offer lovely views of the courtyard or gardens with balcony or terrace. Amenities include en suite bathroom with shower, satellite TV, hairdryer, air conditioning, mini bar and tea &amp; coffee making facilities. </p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Rooms </strong>are 29m² and sleep up to three people with views of the pool or garden with balcony or terrace.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms </strong>are 24m² and can accommodate up to three people. They are beautifully furnished with views of the gardens and balcony or terrace.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Sea View Rooms </strong>offer exceptional views out over the pool, gardens and towards the glittering sea just 100 yards away. They can sleep up to three people. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
